	The page includes plenty of information about Adenydd’s work with Big Give over the years and even links back to the main website of the organisation for more information.
	{{ carousel({ carouselId: "prevCampaignsCarousel",
					images: [
						"assets/images/case-studies/Adenydd/prev-campaigns.webp"
