	}}
	All menus artificially expanded via Inspect Element for clarity’s sake. Not an accurate reflection of the site.
	Recategorised pages into projects and services. Also created a “More Projects” submenu to account for projects that were no longer running or relevant. Menu’s are now of a more even size and their items are labelled more descriptively.
</div>

